{
  "text": "Individual supply of energy, macro-and micronutrients was assessed using a 4-day dietary protocol, which discriminated between cooked and uncooked fruits and vegetables [CITATION_1] . Nutritional antioxidant intake by habitual diet was calculated based on the German Food Code and Nutrition Database BLS II.3, additional supply was quantified by a supplement questionnaire.",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "23167135"
